fields.description:
When i run for the IOS simulator everything is fine. When i try to build for deployment....it takes forever to build and sticks on this line "Processing JavaScript files"....and then fails with this error: 

[ERROR] :  /Users/pladis/Documents/LPDevices.nosync/IOS/Resources/ui/handheld/iphoneV2/Services/FormsService.js: Argument name clash in strict mode (3045:115)

Any ideas?
